title: Skrull Kill Krew 01-05 (1995-1996|Digital|AnPymGold-Empire)
description:
Two of the biggest UK names in the business, Mark Millar and Grant Morrison, got their stateside start with this unassuming little gem. Morrison's friend Steve Yeowell (of Zenith fame) did the art, while a behind-the-scenes Brendan McCarthy designed some of the looks and did the covers. Amazing talent for a story about a group of misfits murdering Skrulls left and right! Promotional info - "See where two of Marvel's masters of mutantdom first made their mark! Grant Morrison and Mark Millar co-wrote this chilling story of murderous shape-changing criminals... and the menace they've sworn to cleanse from the Earth! Guest-starring Captain America and Nick Fury!"

Thanks to AnPymGold-Empire for these digital copies, they look great! Please seed, and enjoy! :-)
